                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8284" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0872</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1877 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">果香十八洞：苗汉子果业的资源拼凑之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Fruit Fragrance Shibadong Village: Miaohanzi Fruit&#39;s Entrepreneurial Bricolage Road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郭坤，赵恩铮，李曦文，杨若炎，兰向远，牛振光</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">花垣县十八洞村苗汉子果业有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小乡镇企业；创业资源拼凑；精准扶贫退坡机制；乡村振兴；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Small and medium-sized township enterprises; Entrepreneurial bricolage; Precision poverty alleviation and slope reduction mechanism; Rural revitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本文以十八洞村苗汉子果业为研究对象，展现了精准扶贫政策背景下，苗汉子果业靠种植猕猴桃引领全村脱贫致富的创业历程。本案例侧重于描绘苗汉子果业在初创期、成长期遭遇的重重困难，以及在乡镇企业家石志刚的带领下，企业如何通过资源拼凑突破资源约束，成功创业并取得发展。面对产品同质化与扶贫政策力度减退等新挑战，向读者抛出问题，资源拼凑是否继续适用，企业的未来如何发展。
本案例有助于学生了解资源拼凑理论的相关知识点。包括创业资源的内涵与类型、资源拼凑的内涵、资源拼凑策略、资源拼凑效果、资源拼凑的影响因素以及资源编排理论等。旨在让学生掌握资源约束条件下企业资源拼凑的过程、策略、效果与影响因素，并引起学生思考资源拼凑理论的适用性及资源拼凑理论与资源编排理论的应用路径。本案例为中小乡镇企业突破资源约束提供指导，引发学生对扶贫政策“退坡”背景下，中国乡镇企业探索恰当的乡村振兴之路，走标准化、规范化及模式化的可持续发展之路展开思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case focuses on the Shibadong Village under the &quot;Precision Poverty Eradication&quot; policy, with the background of Shibadong Village&#39;s poverty alleviation through kiwifruit cultivation. The case describes the difficulties in the company&#39;s start-up and growth, and how, under the leadership of township entrepreneur Shi Zhigang and First Secretary Shi Jintong, the company was able to break through the constraints and resolve the crisis through a patchwork of resources. At the same time, in the face of new challenges such as product homogenization and declining poverty alleviation policies, the case raises the question of whether entrepreneurial bricolage is the only strategy and the future direction of the enterprise.
The case is designed to help students understand the theory of entrepreneurial bricolage, and to guide students to think about the applicability of entrepreneurial bricolage and the development path of enterprises. The case not only provides a reference for township enterprises to break through the resource constraints, but also stimulates students to think about how to promote the sustainable development of township enterprises in a standardized, regulated and patterned way, and to explore new paths for rural revitalization in the context of the poverty alleviation policy &quot;retreating from the slope&quot;.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》、《创新与创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资源拼凑理论；资源编排理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-04</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
